text_preview: Create a simple Google Calendar event (all-day or 1-hour timed) in the primary calendar.
在主要行事曆建立簡單事件（整天或 1 小時的定時事件）。
Args: title, year, month, day, time, location.
參數提示：title、year、month、day、time、location。
Create a meeting tomorrow 3–4pm with Alice and Bob at Kelley 2001, send invites.
幫我建立明天 3–4pm 的會議，地點 Kelley 2001，邀請 Alice、Bob 並寄出邀請。
Standup every Monday 9:00–9:15 AM, add a Meet link.
每週一早上 9:00–9:15 的 standup，附上 Meet 連結。
All-day reminder on Friday: Submit assignment.
本週五整天提醒：繳交作業。
Schedule 'Project sync' next Tue 2–3 PM (PDT), invite carol@example.com and dave@example.com, reminder 10 min.
下週二下午 2–3 點建立「Project sync」，時區 PDT，邀請 carol@example.com、dave@example.com，提醒 10 分鐘。
Create a recurring event 'Gym' every Wed and Fri 7–8 AM, no email updates.
建立「健身」每週三與週五 7–8 AM 的重複事件，不寄出郵件通知。
Block off vacation from Aug 21–25, mark as out of office.
8/21–8/25 請假封鎖行程，狀態設為外出（OOO）。
Office hours on March 5 from 1:30–3:00 PM at KEC 1001.
3/5 下午 1:30–3:00 在 KEC 1001 建立 office hours。
Create 'Midterm review' on 2025-10-12 14:00–15:30, add a Meet link and description.
2025-10-12 14:00–15:30 建立「期中複習」，加上 Meet 連結與說明。
Private event 'Doctor appointment' next Thursday 10–11 AM at Samaritan Clinic.
下週四 10–11 AM 建立「看診」私密事件，地點 Samaritan Clinic。
Today at 5 PM create a 30-minute meeting with team@company.com, timezone America/Los_Angeles.
今天 5 PM 和 team@company.com 開 30 分鐘會議，時區 America/Los_Angeles。
Add 'Final presentation' on May 30, 9–11 AM, location MAGRUDER 100, set color to blue.
5/30 9–11 AM 建立「期末簡報」，地點 MAGRUDER 100，顏色設為藍色。
Create '1:1 with Alex' every other Tuesday 4–4:30 PM, send updates.
每隔一週週二 4–4:30 PM 建立「與 Alex 1:1」，寄出更新。
Schedule 'Flight to PDX' on 2025-09-01 06:00–08:00, visibility private; add confirmation code in description.
2025-09-01 06:00–08:00 建立「飛往 PDX」，可見性設為 private，說明加上訂位代碼。
Create 'Study group' Sunday 7–9 PM with five attendees, reminder popup 30 minutes.
週日 7–9 PM 建立「讀書會」，邀請五位參加者，提醒設 30 分鐘彈出通知。
Team lunch next Friday 12:15–1:15 PM at Cafe Yumm, note 'order ahead'.
下週五 12:15–13:15 建立「團隊午餐」，地點 Cafe Yumm，備註「提早點餐」。

Get directions from an origin (or current location) to a destination, returning distance, travel time, and a route summary.
從起點（未提供則使用目前位置）到目的地取得路線，回傳距離、行車時間與路線摘要。
Args: destination, origin, mode, language.
參數提示：destination、origin、mode、language。
How long to walk from Kelley to Valley Library?
從 Kelley 走到 Valley Library 要多久？
Driving route from OSU to Portland avoiding tolls.
從 OSU 開車到 Portland，避開收費道路。
Bike directions to the nearest WinCo.
騎腳踏車去最近的 WinCo 要怎麼走？
Transit route to PDX arriving by 7:30 AM.
搭大眾運輸在早上 7:30 前到 PDX 的路線。
Give me 3 alternatives for driving right now.
現在開車，幫我提供 3 條替代路線。
Driving directions from Corvallis to Eugene via OR-99W.
從 Corvallis 到 Eugene 走 OR-99W 的開車路線。
Leave at 5 PM and drive to downtown Portland—what's the ETA with traffic?
下午 5 點出發開車到 Portland 市中心，考慮路況的抵達時間是多少？
Walking route from Valley Library to KEC avoiding indoor paths.
從 Valley Library 走到 KEC，避開室內通道的步行路線。
Route from OSU to Costco, then to PDX, with Costco as a waypoint.
從 OSU 先到 Costco 再到 PDX，將 Costco 設為中途停靠點。
Optimize waypoints for these stops: Home, Target, Airport.
對『家、Target、機場』這些中途點做最佳化排序。
How many minutes to bike from 1500 SW Jefferson Ave to Valley Library?
從 1500 SW Jefferson Ave 騎腳踏車到 Valley Library 需要幾分鐘？
Transit to OMSI with fewer transfers.
搭大眾運輸去 OMSI，偏好少轉乘。
Bus and rail only to downtown Seattle; arrive by 9 AM.
只搭公車與火車前往西雅圖市中心，上午 9 點前抵達。
Driving directions in Chinese, avoid highways.
請用中文提供開車路線，並避開高速公路。
Walking distance in miles from Kelley to Reser Stadium.
從 Kelley 到 Reser Stadium 的步行距離（英里）。
Navigate to the nearest gas station.
導航到最近的加油站。
Take me to the closest coffee shop.
帶我去最近的咖啡店。
How do I get to an open pharmacy near me right now?
現在有營業的藥局，怎麼走？
Get me directions to the best-rated sushi place nearby.
導航到附近評價最高的壽司店。
Drive to the cheapest supermarket around here.
帶我去這附近最便宜的超市。
Take me to a pizza place within 2 km.
導航到 2 公里內的披薩店。
Route to a ramen shop near campus.
走到校園附近的拉麵店怎麼走？
Guide me to an EV charger near me.
帶我去附近的電動車充電站

Retrieve specific details (address, phone, website, opening hours, etc.) for a place resolved by text query.
以文字查詢解析地點後，取得指定的細節（地址、電話、官網、營業時間等）。
Args: query, fields, language.
參數提示：query、fields、language。
What are the opening hours of Powell's City of Books (Downtown)?
波威爾書城（市中心店）的營業時間是什麼？
What's the phone number for Din Tai Fung (Yongkang)?
鼎泰豐（永康店）的電話是多少？
Give me the website and formatted address for Taipei 101 Observatory.
台北 101 觀景台的官網與正式地址是什麼？
Show the price level and rating for Le Bernardin.
Le Bernardin 的價位等級與評分是多少？
What's the formatted address of Kelley Engineering Center?
Kelley 工程中心的正式地址是什麼？
Provide opening hours and phone for OSU Memorial Union.
OSU 學生活動中心（Memorial Union）的營業時間與電話是什麼？
What's the official website for Valley Rock Gym (Corvallis)?
Valley Rock Gym（Corvallis）的官方網站是什麼？
Tell me the address and opening hours of OMSI.
奧勒岡科學與工業博物館（OMSI）的地址與開放時間是什麼？
Give me the phone number and rating of Starbucks on 5th Ave.
第五大道那間 Starbucks 的電話與評分是多少？
Show the website and user ratings total for Local Boyz Hawaiian Cafe.
Local Boyz Hawaiian Cafe 的官網與評價總數是多少？
What's the official site and phone number for The Broad museum?
The Broad 博物館的官網與電話是多少？
Provide the formatted address and opening hours for the National Taiwan Museum.
國立臺灣博物館的正式地址與開放時間是什麼？
What is the phone number and website of Rogue Bayfront (Newport)?
Rogue Bayfront（Newport）的電話與官網是什麼？
Show the price level and opening hours for Pizzeria Bianco (Town & Country).
Pizzeria Bianco（Town & Country 分店）的價位等級與營業時間是多少？
Give me the address and rating for Alishan House Hotel.
阿里山賓館的地址與評分是多少？

Search for nearby places around the user's current location (cafes, gyms, supermarkets, etc.) with filters.
以「目前位置」為中心搜尋附近地點（咖啡店、健身房、超市等），支援多種篩選。
Args: query, min_rating, min_total_ratings, max_price_level, open_now, rank_by, radius_km, max_results, language.
參數提示：query、min_rating、min_total_ratings、max_price_level、open_now、rank_by、radius_km、max_results、language。
Find highly rated coffee shops near me (rating ≥ 4.5).
找我附近評分 4.5 以上的咖啡店。
Any gyms around me within 2 km?
我附近 2 公里內有什麼健身房？
Restaurants open now near my location.
我這附近現在有開的餐廳。
Cheaper lunch spots near me; rank by distance.
我附近便宜的午餐店，依距離排序。
Best boba nearby with at least 100 reviews.
附近評價數至少 100 的手搖飲店。
Closest gas station open now.
最近而且現在有營業的加油站。
Pharmacies within 3 km that are open now.
3 公里內現在有開的藥局。
Late-night ramen near me.
我附近有沒有宵夜時段的拉麵？
Family-friendly parks around my area.
我附近適合親子的公園。
Dog-friendly cafes near me.
附近有沒有對寵物友善的咖啡店？
Museums within 5 km of my location.
距離我 5 公里內的博物館。
Vegetarian restaurants near me.
我附近的素食餐廳。
Supermarkets with price level up to 1 near me.
我附近價位等級不超過 1 的超市。
Highest-rated bakery nearby with 500+ reviews.
附近評價數 500 以上、評分最高的麵包店。
Find the highest-rated pizza place nearby and take me there.
找附近評價最高的披薩店，帶我去。
Locate a gas station near me and guide me to it.
找最近的加油站，導航過去。
Find an open pharmacy around me and get me directions.
找目前有營業的藥局，幫我規劃路線。
Show a cheap lunch spot close by and navigate me there.
找附近便宜的午餐店，帶我前往。
Find a coffee shop within 1 km and take me there.
找 1 公里內的咖啡店，開始導航。
Pick the nearest ramen place and start directions.
挑最近的拉麵店並開始路線。
Find a supermarket near campus and guide me.
找校園附近的超市，帶我去。
Find any EV charger around here and route me to the closest one.
找附近的電動車充電站，導航到最近的那個。

Create a task in the user's default Google Tasks list with an optional due date/time.
在使用者的預設 Google Tasks 清單建立任務，可選擇設定到期日期/時間。
Args: title, year, month, day, time.
參數提示：title、year、month、day、time。
Add a to-do: Submit assignment by Friday 5 PM.
新增待辦：週五下午 5 點前繳交作業。
Create a subtask under 'Project Alpha' called 'Prepare slides'.
在『Project Alpha』底下新增子任務：準備簡報。
Add 'Buy milk' to my default list with a note: 2% milk.
在預設清單新增『買牛奶』，備註：買 2% 牛奶。
Insert a task right after 'Draft outline' named 'Collect references'.
在『大綱草稿』之後插入任務：蒐集參考資料。
Add a task 'Call mom' for tomorrow at 8 PM.
新增待辦『打電話給媽媽』，時間明天晚上 8 點。
Create 'Renew car insurance' due on 2025-09-15.
建立『續保汽車保險』，到期日 2025-09-15。
Add to the 'School' list: 'Finish lab report'.
在『School』清單新增：完成實驗報告。
Add 'CS531 homework' due next Monday 11:59 PM.
新增『CS531 作業』，下週一晚間 11:59 截止。
Create a subtask under 'Thesis' named 'Outline Chapter 2'.
在『論文』底下新增子任務：第二章大綱。
Add 'Email advisor about project' with a note and a link.
新增『寄信給指導教授討論專題』，加上備註與連結。
Add 'Buy birthday gift for Alex', note 'budget $30'.
新增『幫 Alex 買生日禮物』，備註：預算 30 美元。
Create 'Print tickets' due today at 6 PM.
建立『列印票券』，到期時間今天晚上 6 點。
Add 'Book dentist appointment' due on Sep 3.
新增『預約牙醫』，到期日 9 月 3 日。
Add 'Backup laptop' with link to the instruction page.
新增『備份筆電』，附上教學網頁連結。
Add 'Water the plants' and place it after 'Take out trash'.
新增『澆花』，並排在『倒垃圾』之後。
